sentences.english: Thellonking is one of the most productive activities a human being can undertake.
sentences.chinese: 念考是此中最出產性活動己的總稱能夠舉行。

sentences.english: Europeans simply stole everything and claimed it as their own idea or invention.
sentences.chinese: 歐洲人竊爲己用還聲明是自己的想法或發明。

sentences.english: In order to prepare for the rush from the hall after the notice, has been late.
sentences.chinese: 張伯爲準備從後廳趕上去通知，己經晚了。

sentences.english: He has gone through two pairs of shoes since he went into winter training.
sentences.chinese: 自從他參加冬季體育訓練以來己跑壞了兩雙鞋子。

sentences.english: Oneself are beautiful, said, flower flower also is drunk, why attached to an end?
sentences.chinese: 己說，花開是美，花落亦是醉，何必執着於一種結局？

sentences.english: Free of charge to help customers into the production process.
sentences.chinese: 該工藝非常成熟，己幫多家知名企業導入生產。

sentences.english: Since then the number of milu deer there has greatly increased.
sentences.chinese: 從那以後，那兒的糜鹿的數量己大大增加了。

sentences.english: I will dedicate myself to the Olympic Regatta to be held in my hometown.
sentences.chinese: 我要爲家鄉奧帆賽的舉辦儘自己的一份力量。

sentences.english: The ability to do their work wholeheartedly for the SSI.
sentences.chinese: 儘自己的能力全心全意爲SSI工作。

sentences.english: Except otherwise stated, performance does take into account of reinvestments and capital gain or loss.
sentences.chinese: 除註明外，表現己考慮股息再投資及資本增長及損失。

sentences.english: The perpetration of the crime by the accused was proved to the satisfaction of the court.
sentences.chinese: 法庭確認被告的罪行己得到充分的證實。

sentences.english: Study on the catalytic synthesis of ethyl caproate by sodium hydrogen sulfate;
sentences.chinese: 目的研究硫酸氫鉀在合成己酸己酯工藝中的催化性能。

sentences.english: In business, it's every man for himself.
Instead of buying an expensive new home, we decided to buy an older home amd fix it up ourselves.
sentences.chinese: 我們決定買一間中古屋來自己裝修，以取代買的新屋。

sentences.english: You can customize the clock with any background of your choice.
sentences.chinese: 你可以按照自己選擇的不同背景來自己定做你的鐘。

sentences.english: You started to play hi-fis since you were a student. Has your attitude changed since then?
sentences.chinese: 由學生時代己開始玩音響，到今天的心態可有轉變？
